<section class="newsletter-section">
  <div class="newsletter-section__inner">
    <div class="newsletter-section__images">
      <div class="newsletter-section__illustration newsletter-section__illustration--left"></div>
      <div class="newsletter-section__illustration newsletter-section__illustration--right"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="newsletter-section__content">
      <h2>Få fat i de gode øl... før din nabo opdager dem</h2>
      <p>Tilmeld dig vores nyhedsbrev</p>

      <form class="newsletter-form">
        <input type="email" placeholder="e-mail" />
        <button type="submit">TILMELD DIG HER</button>
      </form>

      <small>“God øl er ikke en nabokrig værd — tip din nabo”</small>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>